channel.description:
I've been doing music since like 2-3 years, maybe even less. Check this chilled out song I've uploaded to SoundCloud.
https://soundcloud.com/cody-march/lets-fly-high
I've also done some Dubstep, Dance, and EDM on there too if you'd like to check those out as well.
